  "texts": [
    "The setup and results of our experimental evaluation are reported in Sects.",
    "4 and 5, while Sect. 6 concludes the paper and outlines areas of future work.",
    "Related workThis section outlines datasets for sentence classification in scientific texts and describes machine learning methods for this task.",
    "Furthermore, we briefly review transfer learning methods.",
    "For a more comprehensive overview of information extraction from scientific text, we refer to Brack et al. [11] and Nasar et al."
  ]
